      <title>字符集、校对集</title>
      <link>https://www.niuwx.cn/posts/mysql/%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6%E9%9B%86%E5%92%8C%E6%A0%A1%E5%AF%B9%E9%9B%86/</link>
